Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:39.88,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてくれたキミとなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.13,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.30,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
