Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:59.22,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們都活在寸步難移的網中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:02.43,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}尋覓你  每當風吹過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:05.67,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中激情彷彿隨風躍動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.10,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}And all of my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:12.09,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一切皆為與你相會的前奏
