Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.13,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.30,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:45.78,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眼前景色將煥然一新
